t=\"_blank\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/logo_instagram.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"icon youutbe\">\n        <a href=\"https://youtube.com/@ishimoto.kyu-syoku?si=SprepLiyML4hAXR7\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/logo_icon_youtube.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"icon line\">\n        <a href=\"https://line.me/R/ti/p/@009zpfth?oat_content=url\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/logo_icon_line.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div><!--  header end --->\n\n</header>\n\n<!-- mainvisual start ---------------------------------------------------------------------------->\n<div class=\"mainvisual\">\n    <div class=\"slider\">\n      <div class=\"image-area vs1\" style=\"background:url(https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/mainvisual01.jpg)left center; background-size:cover;\"> </div>\n      <div class=\"image-area vs2\" style=\"background:url(https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/mainvisual02.jpg)right 45% center; background-size:cover;\"> </div>\n      <div class=\"image-area vs3\" style=\"background:url(https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/mainvisual03.jpg)right 50% center; background-size:cover;\"> </div>\n      <div class=\"image-area vs4\" style=\"background:url(https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/recruit_mainvisual01.jpg)center top; background-size:cover;\"> </div>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"maincopy-area\">\n    <h2 class=\"maincopy\"><img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/maincopy.png\"></h2>\n  </svg>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- contents start ---------------------------------------------------------------------------->\n<div class=\"contents top\">\n\n\n\n<div class=\"block-consept\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"img-area\">\r\n        <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img01.png\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"text-area\">\r\n<p class=\"\">私たち石本商事は、<br class=\"\">\r\n病院・福祉施設・学校における<br class=\"\">\r\n給食の調理受託、および<br class=\"\">\r\n社員食堂・学生食堂においての<br class=\"\">\r\n運営管理・調理受託を<br class=\"\">\r\n行っています。</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"block-news\">\r\n<span class=\"eng-title\">NEWS</span>\r\n<h3 class=\"htext01\">お知らせ</h3>\r\n\r\n <ul class=\"info-list\">\n\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/revruiting/274/\"><span class=\"date\">2024.11.28</span>\n\t<span class=\"category-name\">\n\t\t採用情報\t</span><br>\n\t本社にて「お仕事相談会」開催！</a></li>\n\n\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/revruiting/238/\"><span class=\"date\">2023.08.25</span>\n\t<span class=\"category-name\">\n\t\t採用情報\t</span><br>\n\tハイブ長岡で個別説明会を開催します（8/25(金)・9/1(金)）</a></li>\n\n\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/revruiting/199/\"><span class=\"date\">2023.07.31</span>\n\t<span class=\"category-name\">\n\t\t採用情報\t</span><br>\n\t本社にてお仕事相談会開催！（8/1～10）</a></li>\n\n\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/revruiting/206/\"><span class=\"date\">2023.07.31</span>\n\t<span class=\"category-name\">\n\t\t採用情報\t</span><br>\n\t準社員募集中！（特別養護老人ホーム ブナの里）</a></li>\n\n </ul>\n\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"btn01 detail\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/information\">お知らせ一覧はこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--\r\n<div class=\"bnr-insta\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ishimoto_shouji/?igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"[template_url]/images/bnr_insta.jpg\"></a></div >-->\r\n\r\n\r\n  <div class=\"sns-bnr\">\r\n    <div class=\"icon insta\">\r\n      <a href=\"https://instagram.com/ishimoto_shouji?igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n        <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/logo_instagram.png\" alt=\"\"><br>Instagram</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"icon youutbe\">\r\n      <a href=\"https://youtube.com/@ishimoto.kyu-syoku?si=SprepLiyML4hAXR7\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/logo_icon_youtube.png\" alt=\"\"><br>YouTube</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"icon line\">\r\n        <a href=\"https://line.me/R/ti/p/@009zpfth?oat_content=url\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/logo_icon_line.png\" alt=\"\"><br>LINE</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"block-aboutus\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"text-area\">\r\n        <span class=\"eng-title\">ABOUT US</span>\r\n<h3 class=\"htext01\">石本商事について</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">「安全で美味しい食事を提供し続ける」を目指す、当社の概要について紹介します。</p>\r\n<p class=\"btn01 detail\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/company\">詳細はこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img-area shadow\">\r\n        <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img02.jpg\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-service\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"text-area\">\r\n        <span class=\"eng-title\">SERVICE</span>\r\n<h3 class=\"htext01\">サービス内容について</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text01\">当社が提供する各種給食の調理受託・運営管理サービスについて紹介しています。</p>\r\n<p class=\"btn01 detail\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/service\">詳細はこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flex\">\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n          <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img21.jpg\" alt=\"衛生管理\" class=\"shadow\">\r\n<span class=\"box-title\">Promise1</span>\r\n<h4>衛生管理</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">安全・安心も、私たちの品質。厳しい視線で衛生管理に取り組んでいます。</p>\r\n<p class=\"arrow01\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/service/#promise01\">詳しくはこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n          <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img22.jpg\" alt=\"品質管理\" class=\"shadow\">\r\n<span class=\"box-title\">Promise2</span>\r\n<h4>品質管理</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">マニュアルの徹底、チーフマネージャー・栄養士による定期巡回により、きめ細かな現場管理を実施しています。</p>\r\n<p class=\"arrow01\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/service/#promise02\">詳しくはこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n          <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img23.jpg\" alt=\"メニュー計画\" class=\"shadow\">\r\n<span class=\"box-title\">Promise3</span>\r\n<h4>メニュー計画</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">彩りや季節感を盛り込み、全ての人に温もりの伝わる食事を提供します。</p>\r\n<p class=\"arrow01\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/service/#promise03\">詳しくはこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-process\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"text-area\">\r\n        <span class=\"eng-title\">PROCESS</span>\r\n<h3 class=\"htext01\">導入までのプロセス</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">サービス導入までの流れを紹介しています。ご覧の上お気軽にお問い合わせください。</p>\r\n<p class=\"btn01 detail\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/process\">詳細はこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img-area1\">\r\n        <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img31.jpg\" class=\"shadow\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"img-area2\">\r\n        <img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img32.jpg\" class=\"shadow\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block-recruit\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"text-area\">\r\n        <span class=\"eng-title\">RECRUIT</span>\r\n<h3 class=\"htext01\">採用情報</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text01\">私たちと一緒に石本商事で働きませんか？<br class=\"\">\r\n食を通じて人々を元気にする誇りある仕事です。各採用に関する情報はこちらよりご覧ください。</p>\r\n<p class=\"btn01 green1\"><a href=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/recruit\">採用情報はこちら</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"btn01 green2\"><a href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/22/pc/search/corp87510/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">新卒エントリーはこちら</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"btn01 green2\"><a href=\"https://isimotoshouji-saiyo.jp/-/top/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">中途・パート採用はこちら</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img-area1\">\r\n<img src=\"https://www.isimotoshouji.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/ishimoto_temp/images/top_img4.jpg\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"insta\">\r\n\n<div id=\"sb_instagram\"  class=\"sbi sbi_mob_col_2 sbi_tab_col_3 sbi_col_4 sbi_width_resp\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px;\"\t data-feedid=\"*1\"  data-res=\"auto\" data-cols=\"4\" data-colsmobile=\"2\" data-colstablet=\"3\" data-num=\"12\" data-nummobile=\"12\" data-item-padding=\"5\"\t data-shortcode-atts=\"{&quot;feed&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\"  data-postid=\"5\" data-locatornonce=\"000e336bd3\" data-imageaspectratio=\"1:1\" data-sbi-flags=\"favorLocal,ajaxPostLoad,gdpr\">\n\t\n\t<div id=\"sbi_images\"  style=\"gap: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t<div id=\"sbi_load\" >\n\n\t\t\t<button class=\"sbi_load_btn\"\n\t\t\ttype=\"button\" >\n\t\t\t<span class=\"sbi_btn_text\" >さらに読み込む</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"sbi_loader sbi_hidden\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t</button>\n\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"sbi_follow_btn sbi_custom\" >\n\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\"\n\t\t\t\trel=\"nofollow noopener\"  href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ishimoto_shouji/\" style=\"background: rgb(64,139,209);\">\n\t\t\t\t<svg class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-instagram fa-w-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-fa-processed=\"\" aria-label=\"Instagram\" data-prefix=\"fab\" data-icon=\"instagram\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\">\n                    <path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M224.1 141c-63.6 0-114.9 51.3-114.9 114.9s51.3 114.9 114.9 114.9S339 319.5 339 255.9 287.7 141 224.1 141zm0 189.6c-41.1 0-74.7-33.5-74.7-74